      "acceptanceCriteria": "Blood samples from multiple donors spanning clinical haematocrit range; inter-sample variability quantified and propagated.",
      "rationale": "Experimental hemolysis data collected from single pooled bovine blood sample. Inter-donor and inter-species variability not characterised. At MRL 5 this is an unacceptable epistemic gap. Achieved Gradation 1."
